Step 1: Draw a round fluffy head in the center.
Step 2: Add two small triangular ears on top of the head.
Step 3: Draw two big round eyes with tiny dots inside, positioned in the upper part of the head.
Step 4: Add a small curved nose below and between the eyes.
Step 5: Draw a rounded body shape connected below the head.
Step 6: Add four short legs extending down from the body.
Step 7: Draw a long curved tail coming from the back right side of the body.